<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.218128>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. 1. Hexoplon rubriceps sp. nov., holotype female, length 15.5 mm; 2. Gnomidolon pulchrum Martins, 1960, female (ACMS), lengh 11.9 mm; 3. Cycnidolon praecipuum sp. nov., holotype female, length 6.9 mm; 4. Pteroplatus caudatus sp. nov., holotype male, length 11.8 mm; 5. Pteroplatus pallidicolor sp. nov., holotype male, length 13.0 mm; 6. Eurysthea parva sp. nov., holotype female, length 10.3 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/218128/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

